CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 13, 1957, pg. 13 reads: "Daisy E. Lampkin Lauded for Service to Mankind At Colorful Testimonial in Webster Hall - Speaker - Thurgood Marshall chats with Mayor David L. Lawrence of Pittsburgh, during the heart-warming testimonial given for Daisy Lampkin last week"
TitMainTitle: Thurgood Marshall, Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence, Jessie Vann, and Roy Wilkins, seated behind banquet table in Webster Hall for honoree Daisy Lampkin
